summary: OpenAI is hosting its first developer conference, OpenAI DevDay, on November 6, 2023 in San Francisco. The event will allow developers to preview new tools and exchange ideas with the OpenAI team. Attendees can join breakout sessions led by OpenAI's technical staff. OpenAI's API has been continuously updated to include advanced models like GPT-4, GPT-3.5, DALL·E, and Whisper, which are being used by over 2 million developers for various applications. CEO Sam Altman is excited to showcase the latest work. More information can be found at devday.openai.com.
